programme.title: Pinggan Tak Retak Nasi Tak Dingin Ep19
programme.desc: Memaparkan Hani dan Mizan yang semakin mesra berada bersama keluarga mereka di rumah keluarga Sheila. Bapa Sheila masih terlantar dan ibunya masih tidak sedarkan diri di hospital. Hubungan Sheila dengan Nizam masih dingin dan tegang. Mereka sering bertengkar tidak di hadapan ibu dan bapa Nizam. Dalam keadaan begitu semasa perbincangan keluarga, Sheila memberani diri meminta Nizam agar dapat menguruskan segala urusan kerja bapa Sheila yang penting. Ibu dan bapa Nizam serta disokong Mizan menggalak sedemikian. Nizam yang masih ada hati terhadap Hani mencadangkan Hani turut bekerja bersamanya. Hani tidak membuat keputusan, tetapi berhelah kononnya dia mengalami tanda tanda mengandung. Dia bergegas ke bilik air dan dituruti Mizan yang benar benar hendak membantu, langsung mereka hanya berpakat sedemikian. Sementara itu, Shariff yang sering mengingati Hani menghubunginya dan memaklumkan dia terpilih tawaran bekerja. Hani tidak memberi sebarang ketetapan. Sheila diugut Nizam dan meminta bayaran kerana bersetuju berbaik berlakon sebagai suami. Kebetulan ibu Sheila telah sedar dan menerima dengan bersyukur Nizam apabila Sheila memperkenalkan sebagai suaminya. Hani dan Mizan terus mesra dan mereka banyak berkomunikasi dan kedua mereka membeli sedikit barang keperluan untuk menemui Yusri, adik dan atuknya.

programme.title: Cintaku Di Bumi Izmir Ep16
programme.desc: Suzan kecewa dan anggap Aidid saja rahsiakan hal itu. Sh Kamariah bawa Suzan balik KL untuk selesaikan masalah ni. Tapi demi jaga aib Haryati, Aidid teruskan nikah. Haryati dan Juliana ambil kesempatan saiko Suzan supaya dia tarik diri dan tinggal Aidid. Suzan juga ugut Aidid, dia akan balik Izmir jika Aidid tak tunai janji untuk cerai Juliana lepas nikah nanti. Mujur Sh Kamariah ada jaga Suzan. Dan bila dia dapati Juliana adalah anak Sherry, Sh Kamariah faham yang Aidid adalah mangsa. Di hari pernikahan, Aidid nampak serba-salah nak teruskan majlis nikah atau tak.

programme.title: Pinggan Tak Retak Nasi Tak Dingin Ep16
programme.desc: Memaparkan Shariff terus meminati Hani dia memujuk Yusri untuk menceritakan sejauh mana hal Hani. Dalam masa yang sama Shariff ada masalah keluarga berpunca bapanya. Dia juga akui kepada Dzul dan pernah menghubungi Hani untuk temujanji, tetapi Hani tegas menolak. Nizam yang baru bekerja di Johor Bahru menerima kunjungan mengejut Sheila. Di peringkat mula Nizam bukan sahaja memarahi Sheila tetapi tidak mahu menerima kedatangan dan melayannya. Dia juga mengherdik dengan kata-kata kesat. Sehingga Sheila merayu agar memberi ruang dan peluang akhirnya terbuka juga hati Nizam. Lantaran itu, Sheila berkesempatan memberi tahu secara serius kepada Nizam bahawa Mizan amat sayangkan Hani dan lupakan sahaja hasratnya. Setakat ini Nizam masih tidak percaya. Apa pun dia juga menyatakan kepada Sheila dia akan mencari rumah mereka di Johor Bahru dan meminta Sheila pulang. Mizan delima kerana membayangkan keadaan yang amat tidak sesuai berlaku jika Sharif rakan baiknya menghawini Hani dan mereka pula sepejabat. Dalam pada itu Suraya pula cuba mengapi-apikan rumah tangganya. Antara Mizan dengan Hani masih dingin, tetapi Hani lebih tenang dan masing-masing tidak abaikan tanggungjawab rumah tangga.

Datin Fairuz memberi amaran kepada Leto agar tidak berkawan dengan Stila lagi. Dia juga memberitahu Mak Tini hal yang sama. Akibatnya, mak Tini menyuarakan bantahannya apabila Stila datang ke rumah. programme.title: Pinggan Tak Retak Nasi Tak Dingin Ep18
programme.desc: Memaparkan semua keluarga Hani ada di rumahnya. Nizam mahu tidak mahu terpaksa menerima Sheila dan anaknya tidur sebilik. Sementara itu hubungan Hani dan Mizan yang mesra seperti bukan berlakon lagi. Dalam pada itu Nizam tetap menyukai Hani dan Hani tahu mengelak dan berbalas cakapnya. Mereka sekeluarga juga ke hospital. Di hospital, hubungan Nizam dan Sheila masih tegang. Nizam berterus terang dia hanya berlakon jika berjumpa dengan ibu Sheila kerana dia akan berkahwin dengan Hani dan Sheila tetap akan diceraikan. Demi untuk nampak tenang, Sheila mengalah, sanggup terima apa yang dihajat Nizam. Walau pun begitu dia meminta masa. Sheila melawat ibunya di wad, walau pun dia berkata-kata telah berkahwin dan memohon maaf tetapi ibunya tidak sedar ketika itu. Sheila juga bersemuka sekali lagi dengan Hani dan terang-terang Hani menafikan segala hasrat Nizam dan didengari Nizam. Sementara itu Shariff tetap menyukai Hani dan meminta bantuan ibu saudaranya Umairah isteri Datuk Fuad menjadi wakilnya agar Hani kelak menjadi isterinya. Dalam masa yang sama Datuk Fuad, suami Umairah curang telah mengamalkan rasuah membolehkan Ah Meng mudah perolehi tender sepatutnya diperolehi syarikat mereka. Semuanya gara-gara Suraya. Berikutan itu Shariff diminta Umairah utamakan menyelamatkan syarikat mereka. Umairah juga memaklumkan Shariff berdasarkan biodata Hani, Hani itu adalah adik kandungnya.

programme.title: Pinggan Tak Retak Nasi Tak Dingin Ep19
programme.desc: Memaparkan Hani dan Mizan yang semakin mesra berada bersama keluarga mereka di rumah keluarga Sheila. Bapa Sheila masih terlantar dan ibunya masih tidak sedarkan diri di hospital. Hubungan Sheila dengan Nizam masih dingin dan tegang. Mereka sering bertengkar tidak di hadapan ibu dan bapa Nizam. Dalam keadaan begitu semasa perbincangan keluarga, Sheila memberani diri meminta Nizam agar dapat menguruskan segala urusan kerja bapa Sheila yang penting. Ibu dan bapa Nizam serta disokong Mizan menggalak sedemikian. Nizam yang masih ada hati terhadap Hani mencadangkan Hani turut bekerja bersamanya. Hani tidak membuat keputusan, tetapi berhelah kononnya dia mengalami tanda tanda mengandung. Dia bergegas ke bilik air dan dituruti Mizan yang benar benar hendak membantu, langsung mereka hanya berpakat sedemikian. Sementara itu, Shariff yang sering mengingati Hani menghubunginya dan memaklumkan dia terpilih tawaran bekerja. Hani tidak memberi sebarang ketetapan. Sheila diugut Nizam dan meminta bayaran kerana bersetuju berbaik berlakon sebagai suami. Kebetulan ibu Sheila telah sedar dan menerima dengan bersyukur Nizam apabila Sheila memperkenalkan sebagai suaminya. Hani dan Mizan terus mesra dan mereka banyak berkomunikasi dan kedua mereka membeli sedikit barang keperluan untuk menemui Yusri, adik dan atuknya.

Namun kerana gejala dadah, masalah peribadi yang tidak terkawal dan kemalangan ngeri yang menimpa, kehidupan anggota kumpulan musnah. programme.title: Plan B Ep6
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Khai dan Mika cuba berlatih menembak beberapa sasaran ke arah botol dari pistol yang dicuri oleh Mika milik ayahnya dan dia merancang untuk merompak syarikat ayahnya. Sementara itu Dr. Rizman cuba berbincang dengan isteri mengenai anak tunggalnya, Khai, setelah dia mendapati Khai sudah tersasar jauh daripada keluarga. Dr.Rizman juga mengakui dia telah mengabaikan tanggung jawabnya terhadap Khai. Namun Khai menolak segala bentuk bantuan daripada kedua-dua ibu bapanya, walaupun ibunya mengakui kesilapan mereka yang lalu. Kemudian Khai tidak dapat menerima hakikat, kenapa ibu bapanya bersikap demikian terhadapnya dan merasakan seolah-olah dia bukan anak kepada ayahnya, Dr.Rizman.

programme.title: Chikaro
programme.desc: Mengisahkan seorang gadis kampung naif yang datang ke bandar untuk mencari pekerjaan di sebuah pejabat dan di situ dia telah bertemu dengan bekas mat rempit yang telah jatuh cinta pada pandangan pertama. Dia berusaha untuk menolong gadis itu sesuaikan diri dengan gaya hidup bandar dan akhirnya gadis kampung itu juga telah jatuh cinta kepadanya. Walaubagaimanapun kerana sifatnya yang matang, ramai wanita mencemburuinya.

programme.title: Tom Yum Goong
programme.desc: Tom yum goong (2005) ialah filem Thai,Inggeris,Mandarin,Vietnam. Prachya Pinkaew telah mengarahkan filem ini. Tony Jaa,Nathan Jones,Xing Jin,Petchtai Wongkamlao adalah pelakon filem ini. Ia telah dikeluarkan pada tahun 2005. Tom yum goong (2005) dianggap sebagai salah satu filem Aksi, Jenayah, Drama, Thriller terbaik di India dan di seluruh dunia.

programme.title: You Saka..Pergi Jauh-jauh S1 Ep12
programme.desc: Episod ke 12 ini memaparkan antara lain Adrus masih berkeadaan tidak normal. Kali ini kelakuan agresifnya hingga menyebabkan badannya bertukar bentuk dan warna kulitnya hijau seperti 'Hulk'. Sambil itu dia mengancam ahli keluarganya, tetapi dengan keberanian Nia berdepan, di samping memohon perkara yang tidak baik dihindarkan, tiba-tiba Adrus berubah kepada asal, tetapi masih tidak sedar diri. Ibrahim, isterinya dan Pak Abas terus membincangkan tentang Gelam yang bersifat meresapi dalam jiwa manusia. Lantaran itu manusia berkenaan akan gelisah. Situasi itulah dialami Zeti, malahan dia juga bercakap dalam dua nada. Sementara itu Datin Salina selain dalam ketakutan kerana terserempak dengan lembaga putih, dia mula bercakap berseorangan. Lebih parah, pejabatnya menerima notis untuk di sita. Nia telah menemui Fauzan setelah dia diminta membantu. Sebelum itu, Adrus telah kembali normal dan pulih. Dia bersama bapanya mengekori Nia bimbangkan sesuatu terjadi.

programme.title: UC 5
programme.desc: Salih ditembak dengan senapang di hutan tempat dia pergi berburu bersama rakannya Metin. Salih, yang terpaksa hidup dengan peluru di otaknya, memerlukan bantuan material dan rohani untuk sembuh. Metin, yang mengatakan bahawa dia akan melakukan semua jenis bantuan kepada Salih pada mulanya. Kemudian bertunang dengan teman wanita Salih iaitu Sermin, meninggalkan Salih dengan ibunya sendirian. Arzu, bekas tunang Metin, tidak dapat memahami apa yang berlaku. Semasa cuba mencari tahu mengapa Metin berkelakuan sedemikian, Salih dan ibunya, seorang wanita luar biasa, melawat Türkan.

programme.title: Budak Magik Ep7
programme.desc: Memaparkan kisah bagaimana Imran dan Haikal berjaya menemui batu permata yang sedang dicari oleh seorang bekas banduan dikenali dengan nama Hariman. Hariman dibantu oleh Salim, pemilik kedai runcit, untuk mencari permata yang mereka percaya masih tersembunyi dalam kawasan hutan dihujung kampung. Sementara itu Haikal telah membahagi-bahagikan hasil penemuannya kepada Imran, Maira dan Zara tanpa mengetahui nilai sebenar permata yang mereka miliki. Rahsia mereka memiliki permata yang sedang dicari oleh Hariman terbongkar apabila Imran menyerahkan sebiji permata kepada Salim untuk membayar guli berharga RM 12 yang dibeli dari kedai Salim kerana dia terlupa membawa wang. Salim yang begitu teruja segera pergi berjumpa Hariman yang teramat gembira apabila melihat permata yang ditunjukkan oleh Salim kepadanya.

programme.title: Seekers Underground Ep1314
programme.desc: Seekers kembali dengan nama baru Seekers Underground. Dengan teknologi baru serta tinjaun ke lokasi yang belum pernah diterokai

programme.desc: Seorang gadis yang mempunyai 3 rakan hantu kini tinggal bersama kakaknya yang semakin malu dengan keupayaan gadis itu untuk melihat hantu.

programme.title: Bodyguard S1 Ep12
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Ryan diupah sebagai bodyguard kepada Yasmin oleh bapanya. Yasmin dilarang dari berjumpa dengan Hakim kerana ibu Hakim mempunyai sejarah silam yang menyakitkan dengan bapa Yasmin. Dalam kes berasingan, Rahul telah diupah oleh Datin untuk mengintip kegiatan Dato’ Rahman. Dato’ dikatakan mempunyai skandal dengan perempuan lain. Nasha telah meminta Danial menjaga Harris yang selalu diganggu oleh along. Danial mendapati Harris menjadi penjamin kepada rakannya Anuar untuk meminjam wang along tetapi tidak membayar balik wang tersebut. Anuar memberitahu wang tersebut telah dirompak, mereka telah diarahkan oleh Nasha membuat laporan polis. Sementara itu, hubungan Farish dengan Nasha kembali pulih.

programme.title: Danur2: Maddah
programme.desc: Seorang gadis yang mempunyai 3 rakan hantu kini tinggal bersama kakaknya yang semakin malu dengan keupayaan gadis itu untuk melihat hantu.

programme.title: Plan B Ep5
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Khai kalah dalam perlumbaan kereta "drift". Dia tidak mampu membayar wang taruhan sebanyak RM50 ribu lalu mengadai kereta lumbanya. Di rumah Khai terperangkap ketika dia cuba membuka peti besi wang bapanya. Dia dihalau dari rumah. Kemudian Khai berjaya meminjam wang daripada rakannya, Mica dan menebus kembali keretanya yang tergadai itu. Khai tidak pulang ke rumah hanya tidur dalam kereta yang dipakirnya di tepi jalanraya.

programme.title: Sacred Riana 2: Bloody Mary
programme.desc: Riana ke asrama sekolah Elodia dengan harapan dapat mencari anak patung Riani yang hilang. Para pelajar di situ sering melakukan ritual dengan cermin, iaitu Bloody Mary. Ia yang pada asalnya hanya untuk menakutkan pelajar baru, bertukar menjadi bencana apabila roh cuba mencederakan pelajar. Anak patung Riani didakwa sebagai dalang di sebalik bencana ini. Riana terperangkap dalam dilema antara membawa balik anak patungnya, atau mencari jawapan kepada pelbagai ketakutan yang berlaku.

programme.title: Budak Magik Ep7
programme.desc: Memaparkan kisah bagaimana Imran dan Haikal berjaya menemui batu permata yang sedang dicari oleh seorang bekas banduan dikenali dengan nama Hariman. Hariman dibantu oleh Salim, pemilik kedai runcit, untuk mencari permata yang mereka percaya masih tersembunyi dalam kawasan hutan dihujung kampung. Sementara itu Haikal telah membahagi-bahagikan hasil penemuannya kepada Imran, Maira dan Zara tanpa mengetahui nilai sebenar permata yang mereka miliki. Rahsia mereka memiliki permata yang sedang dicari oleh Hariman terbongkar apabila Imran menyerahkan sebiji permata kepada Salim untuk membayar guli berharga RM 12 yang dibeli dari kedai Salim kerana dia terlupa membawa wang. Salim yang begitu teruja segera pergi berjumpa Hariman yang teramat gembira apabila melihat permata yang ditunjukkan oleh Salim kepadanya.

programme.title: Binhi
programme.desc: Daniel dan Cynthia, pasangan muda dengan anak dalam perjalanan, mengalami masa sukar di Manila. Mereka kembali ke Baguio, tempat asal Daniel, untuk memulakan semula. Melalui kebaikan Alex, kawan Daniel zaman kanak-kanak yang kaya, mereka dapat tinggal di sebuah rumah besar, tanpa sewa; dan dia mendapat tawaran kerja juga. Segala-galanya seolah-olah jatuh pada tempatnya untuk mereka - atau begitulah yang mereka fikirkan - sehingga perkara aneh mula berlaku di rumah mereka.

programme.title: Muzium Misteri Ep7
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Bad pada mulanya bersiar-siar dan Nur, anaknya pula memesan ayam golek. Bad singgah di Kg. Paling Sweet, di gerai Leman dan membeli ayam golek. Dari Leman maklumat tentang lembaga Senyum diperolehi. Encik Bad berminat dengan kisah itu, setelah mendapat maklumat lanjut dia telah mengarahkan ketiga-tiga pekerjanya supaya mendapat maklumat selanjutnya dari Leman. Yang penting misi mereka menangkap lembaga Senyum. Adam, Daniel dan Shah telah ditunjukkan rumah asal lembaga Periang, bapa lembaga Senyum. Selain itu Leman menceritakan serba ringkas latar belakang lembaga Periang dan beberapa mangsa pernah diganggu oleh lembaga senyum. Berikutan itu Adam, Shah dan Daniel telah masuk ke kawasan kampung itu dengan kereta lengkap dengan peralatan serta keupayaan mereka untuk memerangkap lembaga senyum. Sementara itu Nur terus menjadi tali penghubung di antara bapa dan ibunya. Bapanya menerima kiriman ibunya, tetapi menunjukkan tidak berapa suka. Waktu lapang, Shah akan menghubungi dengan kekasihnya melalui khidmat pesanan ringkas. Pun begitu tetap merahsiakan kepada Adam.

programme.title: Operasi X
programme.desc: Mengisahkan seorang gadis kampung naif yang datang ke bandar untuk mencari pekerjaan di sebuah pejabat dan di situ dia telah bertemu dengan bekas mat rempit yang telah jatuh cinta pada pandangan pertama. Dia berusaha untuk menolong gadis itu sesuaikan diri dengan gaya hidup bandar dan akhirnya gadis kampung itu juga telah jatuh cinta kepadanya. Walaubagaimanapun kerana sifatnya yang matang, ramai wanita mencemburuinya.

programme.title: Budak Magik Ep7
programme.desc: Memaparkan kisah bagaimana Imran dan Haikal berjaya menemui batu permata yang sedang dicari oleh seorang bekas banduan dikenali dengan nama Hariman. Salim yang begitu teruja segera pergi berjumpa Hariman yang teramat gembira apabila melihat permata yang ditunjukkan oleh Salim kepadanya.

programme.title: UC 5
programme.desc: Salih ditembak dengan senapang di hutan tempat dia pergi berburu bersama rakannya Metin. Salih, yang terpaksa hidup dengan peluru di otaknya, memerlukan bantuan material dan rohani untuk sembuh. Metin, yang mengatakan bahawa dia akan melakukan semua jenis bantuan kepada Salih pada mulanya. Kemudian bertunang dengan teman wanita Salih iaitu Sermin, meninggalkan Salih dengan ibunya sendirian. Arzu, bekas tunang Metin, tidak dapat memahami apa yang berlaku. Semasa cuba mencari tahu mengapa Metin berkelakuan sedemikian, Salih dan ibunya, seorang wanita luar biasa, melawat Türkan.

programme.title: Danur2: Maddah
programme.desc: Seorang gadis yang mempunyai 3 rakan hantu kini tinggal bersama kakaknya yang semakin malu dengan keupayaan gadis itu untuk melihat hantu.

programme.title: You Saka..Pergi Jauh-jauh S1 Ep13
programme.desc: Episod ke 13 antara lain memaparkan Nia dituruti Fauzan telah mencabar lembaga putih, kemudiannya lembaga putih akui dirinya tewas dan beredar. Sementara itu, Fauzan mendapati secara diam-diam Nia telah menyimpan harta syarikat atas nama Fauzan sebanyak 1.27 juta. Ini membuatkan Fauzan dan ibunya ingin membalas jasanya lalu mereka mengatur agar Nia ditunangkan dengan pemuda disukainya. Sebelum itu Nia dengan memakai pakaian tradisi keluarganya telah menentang Zeti yang masih diresapi Gelam. Zeti tewas dan Gelam yang meresapinya terpisah. Lantaran itu, Gelam juga dihapuskan oleh Nia. Tok Alai yang sering membantu Nia kemudiannya menghilangkan diri sebagai 'Puteri Jarum Pertama'. Akhirnya satu majlis pertunangan antara Adrus dengan Nia berlangsung dengan selamatnya, walau pun pada awalnya kehadiran rombongan Datin Salina disalah sangka oleh Adrus. Datin Salina bukan sahaja membiayai majlis itu tetapi juga semasa majlis resepsi kelak. Akhirnya semua ahli keluarga Nia dan Datin Salina amat gembira.

programme.title: Tom Yum Goong
programme.desc: Tom yum goong (2005) ialah filem Thai,Inggeris,Mandarin,Vietnam. Prachya Pinkaew telah mengarahkan filem ini. Tony Jaa,Nathan Jones,Xing Jin,Petchtai Wongkamlao adalah pelakon filem ini. Ia telah dikeluarkan pada tahun 2005. Tom yum goong (2005) dianggap sebagai salah satu filem Aksi, Jenayah, Drama, Thriller terbaik di India dan di seluruh dunia.

programme.title: Amukan Pocong S1 Ep13
programme.desc: Sementara itu, Dila dan 4 rakannya berkhemah di Sg. Tua. Dila dan rakan-rakan yang tidak tahu tentang kewujudan pocong Long Husin menjadi mangsa gangguan seterusnya selepas tengah malam. Malam itu adalah malam bonus buat Long Husin kerana Dila dan rakan sekhemahnya, Noy tidur bersama. Dila dan Noy menyangkakan rakan lelaki lain sengaja hendak menakutkan mereka tetapi ketia mereka nyenyak tidur, khemah mereka dibuka dan seorang demi seorang Dila dan Noy dibawa pergi. Esoknya, hanya mayat mereka sahaja yang ditemui tidak berapa jauh dari khemah mereka.

programme.title: Jangan Ikut Aku Ep2
programme.desc: Dalam episod akhir ini, Akil bermimpi mengahwini Cikgu Shila dan mendapat seorang cahaya mata dan mereka berdua selalu mendampingi empat saka itu. Sebenarnya, Chikgu Shila telah menjauhi diri daripada Akil kerana kegagalannya memberitahu tentang empat saka yang mendampinginya. Akil berazam menghalau saka-saka tersebut dan minta pertolongan bomoh Anjang Itam. Anjang Itam bersetuju dengan syarat dia mesti serahkan cincin 4 keramat kepadanya. Apabila Akil enggan, Anjang Itam mengugut hendak membunuh Cikgu Shila. Sebelum Anjang Itam sempat berbuat demikian, Siti, anak bomoh Tok Misai memukulnya. Anjang Itam ditangkap polis kerana dialah yang sebenarnya telah membunuh Tok Misai. Akil minta bantuan Pak Sudin untuk menghalau saka-saka tersebut dan menyerahkan cincin 4 keramat itu kepada Pak Sudin yang membuangnya kedalam tasik. Di situ tamatnya riwayat Jendul, Big Foot, Mayang Kasturi dan Kimchi (saka-saka). Pak Sudin menasihati Akil supaya jangan tinggal solat dan banyak membaca quran kerana makhluk halus akan menjauhkan diri daripada dia. Melihat perubahan Akil yang tidak lagi mendampingi saka-saka, Cikgu Shila berbaik semula dengan Akil. Pada suatu hari Akil telah membawa ibunya kerumah Chikgu Shila untuk mengeratkan lagi pertalian keluarga dan mungkin berkesudahan dengan perkahwinan antara Akil dengan Cikgu Shila

programme.title: Santau Merasuk Ep4
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Nina terperanjat apabila pada satu malam, Arifah datang ke rumah bersama Mat. Nina jadi serba salah mahu mengizinkan Mat masuk, kerana Halim tiada di rumah. Tetapi Mat terus merempuh masuk dengan alasan, dia sudah nampak lembaga yang berkeliaran di dalam rumah itu dan diikuti dengan jeritan Echa. Ketika Mat sedang memulihkan semula Echa, Halim pulang dan menyaksikan segalanya. Terjadi pertelingkahan antara Halim dan Mat. AkhirnyaHalim menghalau Mat bersama Arifah keluar dari rumahnya

programme.title: 3AM Ep4
programme.desc: Sekumpulan kawan pergi berkhemah di dalam hutan yang kononnya berhantu walaupun memberi amaran untuk tidak berbuat demikian. Apabila malam tiba dan perkhemahan ditetapkan, hubungan nafsu dan cinta yang rumit antara mereka terdedah, mencetuskan satu siri peristiwa paranormal yang menghukum mereka. Apabila fajar menyingsing, siapa yang akan keluar dari hutan hidup-hidup?

programme.title: Plan B Ep6
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Khai dan Mika cuba berlatih menembak beberapa sasaran ke arah botol dari pistol yang dicuri oleh Mika milik ayahnya dan dia merancang untuk merompak syarikat ayahnya. Sementara itu Dr. Rizman cuba berbincang dengan isteri mengenai anak tunggalnya, Khai, setelah dia mendapati Khai sudah tersasar jauh daripada keluarga. Dr.Rizman juga mengakui dia telah mengabaikan tanggung jawabnya terhadap Khai. Namun Khai menolak segala bentuk bantuan daripada kedua-dua ibu bapanya, walaupun ibunya mengakui kesilapan mereka yang lalu. Kemudian Khai tidak dapat menerima hakikat, kenapa ibu bapanya bersikap demikian terhadapnya dan merasakan seolah-olah dia bukan anak kepada ayahnya, Dr.Rizman.

programme.title: Dendam Sarakit S1 Ep4
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Dina diminta Mariam untuk menggoda Rafiq dan berkahwin dengannya. Semasa keluar makan malam dengan Dina, Rafiq ternampak bayang Sarakit dalam kereta. Pada malam yang sama, Mariam sekali lagi diganggu penjelmaan Sarakit dan Mariam berada dalam ketakutan. Mariam mendesak Rafiq meninggalkan Sarakit yang dikatakan mengamalkan ilmu sihir. Rafiq enggan mempercayai kata-kata ibunya dan pulang ke Sarakit. Di rumah, Sarakit tidak kelihatan dan Rafiq berihat di sofa setelah membeli bahanbahan makanan. Sarakit telah memasak untuk Rafiq dan mengingatkan Rafiq janjinya iaitu tidak akan meninggalkan Sarakit. Sarakit kemudiannya menuduh Rafiq berlaku curang dan Rafiq menafikannya. Rafiq menyakinkan Sarakit bahawa dia hanya mencintai Sarakit seorang sahaja. Rafiq terjaga dan mendapati apa yang berlaku antaranya dan Sarakit hanyalah mimpi

programme.title: The Sacred Riana: Beginning
programme.desc: Pada zaman kanak-kanaknya, Riana tinggal di sebuah bandar kecil bersama bapanya dan ibunya yang menjalankan perniagaan rumah pengebumian. Musibah memerlukan mereka berpindah ke rumah Pakcik Johan di Jakarta dan Riana bertemu dengan anak patung Riani. Riana semakin dewasa dan suatu hari telah dilawati oleh Puan Klara, seorang guru kaunselor di sekolahnya yang ingin mengetahui sebab Riana tidak hadir ke sekolah dan mencadangkan Riana untuk dipulihkan. Musibah menimpa ibu bapa Riana. Puan Klara datang lagi bersama Hendro, Lusi dan Anggi, untuk membantu Riana beramah mesra. Tetapi, kehadiran mereka mencetuskan masalah yang lebih besar; makhluk ganas masa lalu ia melepaskan dan mengganas mereka semua.

programme.title: Muzium Misteri Ep8
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Adam, Shah Daniel meneruskan usaha pengesanan lembaga senyum dengan bantuan Leman. Secara kebetulan mengikut "Whatsapp Group" Leman bahawa lembaga senyum baru ke rumah Mak Jemah. Kumpulan Adam bergegas ke situ. Mereka dapat mengesannya di rumah Mak Jamah beberapa kali tetapi menghilangkan diri. Mereka gagal. Setelah gagal mereka merujuk kepada Prof. Setelah mendapat penerangan dan kaedah, mereka telah menyiapkan beberapa peralatan permainan kanak-kanak demi untuk menangkap lembaga itu. Pun begitu masih gagal. Sementara itu, Nur terus memujuk bapa dan ibunya supaya makan malam dengan alasan mereka telah sekian lama tidak makan bersekali. Adam, Shah dan Daniel yang gagal kali ini mendapat penerangan daripada penjaga "parking", kononnya dia dulunya pawang, Adam dinasihati memakai jubah hitam. Dengan kaedah itu akhirnya Daniel dan Shah berjaya memerangkap lembaga senyum iaitu ketika Adam seolah bertindak sebagai bapanya. Bad terus gembira dan membenarkan mereka bertiga bercuti.

programme.title: Bodyguard S1 Ep13
programme.desc: Mengisahkan Rahul telah mati ditembak semasa kumpulan bodyguard di bawah Nasha membuat operasi di sebuah banglo. Operasi ini adalah untuk mendapatkan maklumat kegiatan peminjam wang di lokasi tersebut. Dalam kes yang lain, Farish sebagai bodyguard kepada pelakon Kasandara mendapat layanan baik dari pelakon tersebut. Ini adalah kerana Kasandara mulai terpikat dengan Farish. Danial sebagai bodyguard kepada Yasmin diminta pergi ke rumah Dato’ Bakar untuk menyiasat kehilangan Yasmin. programme.title: Taste of Life (T) Ep10871088
programme.desc: Chu-Tsai,Chao and his wife Chin-hsiu,Li have five children. Devoted all his life into developing soy sauce products, Chu-Tsai very much hopes that one of his kids can follow his footsteps and take over his business, but he also respects their own passions and aspirations. Because of their father’s invention dream, the Chao brothers’ lives are about to change… Chin-Pang,Chou used to be Chin-Hsiu’s lover, and has been Chu-Tsai’s long-time business rival. Seeing Chu-Tsai not only successfully keep the patents of soy sauce products, but also has all the support and assistance from his children, Chin-Pang, filled with bitterness, has been crushing and attacking Chu-Tsai in every way. Hsin-Ta, Chu-Tsai’s eldest son, couldn’t bear to see his father suffer, so he quit his job to take over the family business. To everyone’s surprise, Chu-Tsai discovers that Hsin-Ta is actually Chin-Pang’s son! Finding out that the enemy is actually his biological father devastated Hsin-Ta, and this also drives a wedge between Chin-pang and his son Hsiao-Ming, as he feels threatened. Chu-tsai’s second son Ying-kai has always set his goal to reach the top of his career. Vacillating between Mei-mei and Ying-hui, Ying-kai also finds himself caught in between the feud of two families; however, this opens new business opportunities for him. On the other hand, Hsin-ta fulfills Chu-tsai’s dream; but he is more confused than ever about family love and romance love… All he knows is that with the family’s support, his determination and conviction, he can build a future of his own!

programme.title: Blessing of Formosa(T) Ep155
programme.desc: The beauty of folklore is all around us in Taiwan, but we often overlook it and fail to appreciate and feel it. The aim of this program is to promote the beauty of Taiwanese folklore and bring folklore to life. This program showcases folk culture regardless of race or religion, and presents travel information in a fun way, combining easy-to-understand folk culture knowledge with the mission of passing on folk culture. The audience can learn more about folk cultural products such as handicrafts, antiques, temple folklore, as well as short stories about the gods, and information about local tourism. It is an educational and entertaining way to travel and learn about folklore.

programme.title: Taste of Life (T) Ep10911092
programme.desc: Chu-Tsai,Chao and his wife Chin-hsiu,Li have five children. Devoted all his life into developing soy sauce products, Chu-Tsai very much hopes that one of his kids can follow his footsteps and take over his business, but he also respects their own passions and aspirations. Because of their father’s invention dream, the Chao brothers’ lives are about to change… Chin-Pang,Chou used to be Chin-Hsiu’s lover, and has been Chu-Tsai’s long-time business rival. Seeing Chu-Tsai not only successfully keep the patents of soy sauce products, but also has all the support and assistance from his children, Chin-Pang, filled with bitterness, has been crushing and attacking Chu-Tsai in every way. Hsin-Ta, Chu-Tsai’s eldest son, couldn’t bear to see his father suffer, so he quit his job to take over the family business. To everyone’s surprise, Chu-Tsai discovers that Hsin-Ta is actually Chin-Pang’s son! Finding out that the enemy is actually his biological father devastated Hsin-Ta, and this also drives a wedge between Chin-pang and his son Hsiao-Ming, as he feels threatened. Chu-tsai’s second son Ying-kai has always set his goal to reach the top of his career. Vacillating between Mei-mei and Ying-hui, Ying-kai also finds himself caught in between the feud of two families; however, this opens new business opportunities for him. On the other hand, Hsin-ta fulfills Chu-tsai’s dream; but he is more confused than ever about family love and romance love… All he knows is that with the family’s support, his determination and conviction, he can build a future of his own!

programme.title: Have A Nice Dream (M) Ep55
programme.desc: Five young professionals with different life skills, team up for two days and one night trip, leading the audiance to explore the good life of nature and the beauty of the land of Taiwan.

programme.title: Way to Health(M) Ep209210
programme.desc: This show invites top medical professionals from different fields to answer questions from the audience. Approved by the medical world, this show is an influential, as well as reliable place to understand more about one’s health.

programme.title: Mr.Player (M) Ep447
programme.desc: Depending on the locations of the missions, Jacky Wu, the leader of the home team, invites various celebrities to take on challenges and bring you excitement every week.

programme.title: The Wonder Woman(M) Ep45
programme.desc: Be a "shark", if you're a woman, to survive in your working and personal relationship? DU,AI-SHA, also known as Shark, is aggressive and ruthless YI,FEI-YANG nickname is "Orca". Orcas kills sharks. That implies the relationship between them. They are friends and foes at the same time. They show no mercy and never surrender. Love comes and goes but friendship lasts forever. AI-SHA doesn't want to lose her best friend YI,FEI-YANG. She doesn't need love, but she needs him.

programme.title: Genghis Khan
programme.desc: Before he became the great Khan he was known as Temüjin, and was deeply in love with his childhood sweetheart Börte. News of Temüjin's father's death disrupted their relationship and as Temüjin heads back home, he faces a sudden attack from his father's former comrades, causing his whole tribe to be destroyed.

programme.title: 12 Golden Ducks
programme.desc: This is a comeback story about the misadventures of a group of gigolos, led by Future, trying to make their mark in Hong Kong. As with any profession, they have their share of setbacks, but their ability to find laughter within the tears reflects the drive, passion and the indomitable spirit of the Hong Kong people.

programme.title: Project Gutenberg
programme.desc: The Hong Kong Police hunts for a counterfeiting gang led by a mastermind known as Painter. The gang is so skillful that it's almost impossible to distinguish between its counterfeit currency and real money. In an effort to find Painter's real identity, the Police recruits artist Lee Man to assist in solving the case.

programme.title: Cross
programme.desc: Lee believes people who commit suicide will go to hell. After his wife killed herself because of cancer, Lee feels the pain of people with suicidal thoughts and thinks of killing them to bring them to heaven. He then kills the four people from a suicidal website. Despite Lee seeing himself acting upon God’s will, his belief is being challenged.

programme.title: Kowloon Walled City
programme.desc: Neng was a street fighter in Northeast China but decides to start a new life in Hong Kong’s Kowloon Walled City. Unfortunately, he is implicated in the fights and conspiracies among the triad forces. When his good friend is hunted down by the triad, Neng must team up with the residents of Kowloon Walled City to fight back and save his friend.

programme.title: She's a Man. He's a Woman.
programme.desc: This is a romantic comedy about a quarrelsome and loving couple whose spirits are being swapped over after a thunderstorm. The sexy lady finds herself carrying an ugly man’s spirit, and vice versa. Can they switch their spirits back, or do they need to get use to the situation for the rest of their lives?

programme.title: Detective Chinatown 3
programme.desc: After the events in Bangkok and New York, Tang Ren and Qin Feng are invited to solve a murder case in Tokyo, but it turns out to be a challenge for the world’s best detectives. While the case has become complicated and confusing since the world’s top detective got involved, a hilarious challenge for the best detectives in Asia has just begun…

programme.title: Till We Meet Again
programme.desc: Ng Ka Wai is hoping that he will see his loving mother Mui again one day. Mui has apparently been avoiding her son for over a decade while Wai is suffering from depression and panic disorder. When his lost memory suddenly returns, he recalls what he has done to his mother - an unforgivable sin leading to the 10-year separation.

programme.title: Monster Hunt
programme.desc: The pregnant queen of the monster realm flees a civil war and lands in human world, near Yung Ning Village. She seeks the help of a wimpy villager to become the surrogate father for her child, Wuba. From the time he was born, little Wuba embarks on a thrilling journey to escape from those who want to capture him at all costs.

programme.title: Dragon Master: Dragon Spell
programme.desc: The Dragon King is locked in a seal by the Dragon Master for 500 years, and his daughter must travel back in time to 500 years ago to kill the Dragon Master, in order to reverse the act. Little did she know that the Dragon King and Dragon Master were close friends back then…

programme.title: In the Mood for Love
programme.desc: “In the Mood for Love” is Wong Kar-Wai’s most acclaimed feature, navigating the subtle love relationship between Chow Mo Wan and Su Li Zhen after both discover their spouses are having an affair.

programme.title: Touch of the Light
programme.desc: A blind but talented pianist Siang encounters an unrecognized but skilful dancer Chieh. Chieh is attracted to the courageous Siang while Siang is fascinated by the adventurous Chieh. Their friendship grows as Siang and Chieh pursue their dreams together. Sandrine Pinna was awarded Best Actress for her role as Chieh in the 2012 Taipei Film Festival.

programme.title: The New Big Boss
programme.desc: A young man seeks out the Wolf, a legendary undefeated warrior. When he sees that the Wolf is now an old man, he prompts him to retell his past glories.

programme.title: A Lifetime Treasure
programme.desc: A peaceful home for the elderly is under attack when a gangster and his cronies attempt to set up traps to take over the home! Little did they know that the five elderlies residing in the home have amazing talents to take them head on.

programme.title: The Lady Improper
programme.desc: Siu Man is divorced by her husband due to her fear of intimacy. After that, she wants to restart her life by taking over her father’s restaurant. Siu Man hires a new chef with unique culinary philosophy that revitalizes her. Tired of the shackles she placed on herself, Siu Man embarks on a journey of self-discovery and sexual liberation.

programme.title: Secret Diary of a Mom To Be, The
programme.desc: A high-flying PR manager and her loving husband swear by a childless lifestyle but she is shocked to learn that she is expecting just when things look bright for a promotion! How would they deal with the unexpected surprises that life throws in their way?

programme.title: Manhunt
programme.desc: In this movie directed by John Woo, lawyer Du goes on the run after he is framed for a murder. Veteran detective Yamura suspects the case to be more complicated than it seems, and while he understands Du better during the hunt, Yamura still doubts his innocence. Is the real killer lurking elsewhere? Is there a hidden conspiracy behind the murder?

programme.title: The Way We Keep Dancing
programme.desc: This sequel of “The Way We Dance” features the plight of Hong Kong’s grassroots performing artists as they fight against the government’s plan to gentrify an industrial district where they settled in.

programme.title: Fearless
programme.desc: This movie is inspired by the true story of real-life hero Huo Yuan Jia. When a fight destroys the reputation of this renowned martial arts champion along with the lives of his family, Huo’s path to redemption brings him face-to-face with the most ferocious opponents in the world.

programme.title: My Love
programme.desc: Adapted from a Korean movie, this is the love story of school swimmer Zhou Xiao Qi and a transfer student You Yong Ci. Zhou falls in love with You at first sight in high school but You leaves suddenly one day without saying goodbye. As fate brings them back together years later, can they get the spark back in their relationship?

programme.title: Shock Wave 2
programme.desc: A series of bomb explosions is causing fear in Hong Kong. Former bomb specialist Feng is found in coma at the crime scene and becomes a suspect. To prove his innocence, he seeks help from his former partner Wen. However, it seems revealing the truth is as risky as disposing a bomb…

programme.title: My Prince Edward
programme.desc: A newly engaged Hong Kong woman tries to rid herself of a secret sham marriage to a mainlander that she was paid for years ago, before she can get married for real. Winner of Best Original Film Score and Best New Director at the 39th Hong Kong Film Awards.

programme.title: Fierce Cop
programme.desc: To save his son who has been kidnapped by human traffickers, police officer Zhang relentlessly hunts them down and accidentally finds himself implicated in a major child abduction case. In the process, he teams up with a mysterious lady to crack the international crime syndicate and rescue his son.

programme.title: Zhongkui Kill Demon Legend
programme.desc: The Heavenly Master trapped the spirit of the Demon King so as to save the world from evil. Before he dies, the trapped spirit is transferred into Zhong Kui. As a half human and half demon, Zhong Kui is torn between good and evil. Which side will he finally choose?

programme.title: The White Storm
programme.desc: Three Narcotics Bureau officers who are good friends get involved in a case with the drug lord. When the operation fails, they must make a devastating decision - two can live, but one must die. Five years later, the two vow to take revenge but end up competing against each other for their own lives. Will brotherhood be sacrificed again?

programme.title: The Calling of a Bus Driver
programme.desc: A girl named Suki fulfills her dream of being a bus driver after breaking up with her boyfriend, who has an affair with her good friend. When Suki is invited to attend her ex-boyfriend’s wedding, she is presented with a chance for revenge – will she take it and turn her life around?

programme.title: New Kung Fu Cult Master 2
programme.desc: In this sequel, Zhang Wu Ji successfully rescued the Six Major sects at Dadu. Nevertheless, the quest for the Dragon Sabre continues as Wu Ji and his three girlfriends set sail for Ice Fire Island. After a series of vicious fights, they finally unveil the secret behind the Heaven Sword and Dragon Sabre.

programme.title: Those Were the Days
programme.desc: Director Wong despises Cantonese movies of the 60s, but accidentally travels back in time to that movie set. He meets Director Chu, who tells him he can return to modern time if someone likes the film he makes. Wong meets four classic movie stars and invites them to star in his new film, but it flops unexpectedly. Can Wong return to the present?

programme.title: The Bravest Escort Group
programme.desc: A band of courageous bodyguards is tasked with escorting the daughter of general, the concubine of the recently deceased Ming emperor Wu Sangui, and her son, who is the last hope of the Ming Dynasty, to safety.

programme.title: Dearest Anita
programme.desc: Based on real events, the movie follows the footsteps of the fans of Hong Kong Canto-pop diva Anita Mui. After the death of the popstar, fans from different walks of life risk arrest to track down handwritten cards, letters and other possessions from Anita Mui to preserve their idol’s memory.

programme.title: Temporary Family
programme.desc: Hong Kong residential property is reported to be the most expensive in the world. Four young Hong Kong residents, each having their own issues, fall into a property speculation trap and are forced to live together in their new flat.

programme.title: The Narrow Road
programme.desc: Chak, a small cleaning company owner, hits tough times during the pandemic. In need of an assistant, he hires a young single mother Candy, who unexpectedly helps him solve many difficulties at work. While life seems to get back on track, a series of cruel realities happen again, but they still bond together to support each other on the narrow road.

programme.title: The Sword And The Lute
programme.desc: In The Sword And The Lute, Kwei Wu (Jimmy Wang Yu) and his partner (Chin Ping) are on a mission to destroy the "Phoenix Lute", a deadly weapon that shoots poisonous needles up to 500 paces and which can only be destroyed by the Kan curved sword...

programme.title: Diary of a Lady-killer
programme.desc: Tycoon Zhou is a playboy who is engaged to be married, but that did not keep him from working his charms on as many ladies as he can. He keeps a diary about his romantic escapades and soon, the women with whom he has been intimate with are being murdered one by one. Zhou becomes the number one suspect by the police but is the killer someone else?

programme.title: Ambitious Kung Fu Girl
programme.desc: The lovely Michelle Mei Suet plays a spoiled girl Szu-szu who ignores her true love Yang Fan (Yuan Te) to go off in search of a swordsman Chin Ko (Chen Kuan-tai) she idolizes. The search sets off one great action scene after another, until she's threatened to be sold into slavery but Yang Fan arrives in the nick of time! This amusing and entertaining variation on the standard kung-fu film is definitely a winner.

programme.title: The Happy Trio
programme.desc: Li Ching plays, Ah Chiao, a girl from a rural village stranded in the city, who befriends a kind-hearted tramp and a retired actor. They are all poor, but Ah Chiao’s fortune change for the better when she becomes a singer. However, she ultimately learns money can't buy happiness.

programme.title: Shadow Girl
programme.desc: A young swordswoman becomes invisible during the day and a monster at night after taking her grandma’s pill. She ruined the wedding of a bandit chief’s daughter using her powers and is hunted down by them for revenge. Will she escape the hunt?

programme.title: The Mermaid
programme.desc: Zhang and Jin’s daughter, Peony, are betrothed at birth but Jin objects to the engagement now. Zhang meets a carp spirit that looks exactly like Peony and they fall in love. When Justice Bao is asked by Jin to distinguish Peony from her replica, he decides to quit the case when he witness the true love between Zhang and the carp spirit.

programme.title: The Savage Five
programme.desc: A group of bandits flees with a stolen safe to a village where they oppress the villagers and force the blacksmith Wei to unlock the safe. Wei refuses and flees to report to officials, while heroes of the town emerge to fight the bandits.

programme.title: A Friend from Inner Space
programme.desc: A young boy whose parents are separated tries to find happiness in life. One day, he meets and befriends a kind-hearted spirit Ren, who decides to make him truly happy by getting his parents back together.

programme.title: Ode to Gallantry
programme.desc: In this surprisingly light-hearted "Venoms" martial arts adventure, a lone wanderer is repeatedly mistaken for someone else and drawn into a number of violent battles.

programme.title: Empress Wu
programme.desc: Wu Ze Tian is a beautiful and talented concubine of Emperor Tang at age 14. She becomes a nun after he died but has two sons with the new Emperor Tang Gao Zong. The Empress asks Wu to team up with her against Consort Xiao, but is set up and dethroned by Wu, who also kills her two sons. After the Emperor’s death, Wu becomes the first woman Emperor.

programme.title: The Deadly Duo
programme.desc: The prince of the Sung Dynasty is captured by the Chin invaders and is guarded by top martial arts masters. It is up to two powerful patriots to fight the overwhelming odds and pull off the impossible: to rescue the royal Prince and get out of the Chin stronghold alive.

programme.title: Heads For Sale
programme.desc: Hua is an upright and brave swordswoman who will stand up against villains and do anything for Luo, the man she loves. When Luo is sent to jail by the corrupted police, she sets out to free him and did not hesitate to chop off two bodyguards’ heads. In the process, she also stumbles across an old enemy of her father who is back seeking revenge.

programme.title: The Reckless Cricket
programme.desc: Inspired by “Drunken Master”, this kung fu comedy features a bumbling martial artist creating a cricket-style fighting arts to fight and defeat the different martial artists who have beaten him before.

programme.title: King Drummer
programme.desc: A young musician Chi Chiang is hired by the manager of a popular band when the group's drummer/leader Charlie, quits to join a rival group. The new drummer becomes an immediate hit, causing Charlie to be very jealous. Furthermore, the young drummer's mother is dead set against him having a music career.

programme.title: The Silent Swordsman
programme.desc: This is adapted from Louis Cha’s “The Book and the Sword”. A young swordsman is tasked to lead a patriotic secret society to fight the traitorous general who colludes with the enemy. At the same time, he encounters a female warrior and two beautiful princesses, and is caught between all their affections for him.

programme.title: Young Lovers
programme.desc: Guitar-playing rich kid, Yang Fan, heads to Japan to join a rock 'n' roll band where he soon finds himself competing for the affections of two beautiful girls.

programme.title: Holy Flame of the Martial World
programme.desc: This internationally popular tale of a brother and sister, seeking vengeance for the death of their parents through using the mythical yin/yang Holy Flame kung-fu technique. It's an outstanding epic choreographed and co-starring lead "Venom" Kuo Chue (aka. Philip Kwok).

programme.title: The Lark
programme.desc: Sixties pop star Carrie Ku plays the "Little Lark" in this romantic-drama of mistaken identity that is a treasure trove of some of the most popular Mandarin songs of all time.

programme.title: Murderer Pursues
programme.desc: Wang Chung was a valued actor long before he became a director, but as a filmmaker, he helped create some of the most interesting thrillers Shaw Brothers ever released - including this fascinating crime saga of a Sino-Vietnamese crime gang. Danny Lee stars as a misunderstood refugee while Ray Lui plays a cop struggling against his own conscience to ensure that justice is upheld.

programme.title: Emperor Chien Lung and the Beauty
programme.desc: Emperor Chien Lung meets a famous courtesan in Suzhou and in order to spend as much time as possible with her, he builds a direct underground tunnel into the Forbidden City. The emperor’s sudden appearances through this direct access shock his people but it is also at this time that he helps the needy and cracks the gambling business in Suzhou.

programme.title: Young Vagabond
programme.desc: It's a fact: the greatest martial arts movie character is Huang Fei-hung. But it's quite possible the second greatest character is "Beggar Su", one of the famous Ten Kwangtung Tigers, and a legendary Ching Dynasty figure. Little known director Liu Shih-yu decided to fill his telling of the character's life story with the best kung-fu actors Shaw Studios had to offer. He reunited the stars of Liu Chia-liang's landmark Dirty Ho -- Gordon Liu Chia-hui, Wang Yu, and Wang Lung-wei--added such other greats as multi-award-winning Ku Feng and Pai Piao, then gave workhorse Lo Chiang his shot as choreographer. Together they made a rare, colorful, action-packed adventure as Beggar Su and his brother train incessantly to defeat the brutally powerful thief called Centipede. Finally, after much death and destruction, Gordon Liu Chia-hui and Wang Lung-wei get a memorable rematch to follow their classic masterpieces in Dirty Ho and Martial Club. The result is not only reminiscent of preeminent director Liu Chia-liang's work, but essentially an homage to him as well!

programme.title: Blue Skies
programme.desc: A young singer Hsiao Yun becomes an overnight sensation after standing in for another singer at the eleventh hour. Her success comes at a heavy price however, when her love with a pianist suffers. On top of this, Hsiao Yun must also deal with the unwanted affections from an influential backer of her show.

programme.title: Gang Master
programme.desc: This is a story about an army out to destroy the Hsien Lung gang of anti-Yuan revolutionaries. Their leader Ru Yi Tu is up against Fu Zhong Yuan, the identified successor of the Hsien Lung gang who must also prove his own legitimacy. The plot thickens with murder, sibling rivalry and shocking discoveries that could change the course of history.

programme.title: Mr Funny - bone
programme.desc: Join Mr Funny bone in a series of comic vignettes as he attempts to win the heart of a dashing lady. Along for the ride is his loyal sidekick Mr Big Potato, a stout fellow who is forever getting into silly mishaps. The pair gets involved in plenty of shenanigans and gags!

programme.title: Return of the Crazy Bumpkins
programme.desc: This sequel makes for more bittersweet laughs and heart-wrenching misfortune, as Ah Niu gets out of the jail to find his true love becoming the wife of an abusive husband, and his uncle further exploits his naive nature.

programme.title: The Dragon Creek
programme.desc: This wuxia murder mystery film talks about a young girl whose father was ruthlessly murdered during China's early republican era. She has a list of villains who have been plotting against her father and together with her elder brother, the young girl sets out on a journey to hunt down the secret serial killer.

programme.title: Puppy Love
programme.desc: To the tune of the Osmonds hit song, this is a story of adolescent playfulness & innocence lost. Two best friends grow up together and teasingly meet two delightfully impish boys leading to the four to flirtatiously intermingle. However, the innocence of partner swapping eventually leads to a roller-coaster bouts of misunderstood emotions.

programme.title: Five Superfighters
programme.desc: A kung fu master and his three students lost everything after they are floored by a bully. To take revenge, the students find ways to learn from other kung fu masters and come back six months later to have a rematch with the bully on their master’s birthday.

programme.title: The Delinquent
programme.desc: This is a coming-of-age tale depicting the lower class Hong Kong troubled youths in the 1960s and the societal issues that they face. Wang Chung is a hotheaded and rebellious teen who is tempted by the dark side, and have to unfortunately pay a huge price for it.

programme.title: Brothers Five
programme.desc: The five Kao brothers, separated since birth, are unaware that the master of Teng Lung Manor has killed their father. All five however, vow to defeat the vicious gangsters at the manor due to their bullying ways. After reuniting and with much discipline and hard work, the Kaos are prepared to face Lung and his gang.

programme.title: Songfest
programme.desc: As its name implies, Songfest is an Eastmancolor-Shawscope costume musical, traditionally Chinese and timeless in content; yet revealing a spirited and modern technique. Shot on location at Taiwan's beautiful Sun-Moon Lake, it's a turbulent romance between a passionate tea picker Sung Yu-lan and a charming fisherman Li Chun-yang.

programme.title: Legend Of The Fox
programme.desc: A young man, Chin, believes he is an orphan, until he meets three men and learns from them that his father was a great swordsman who was killed when he was trying to dispel rumors of a wrongdoing and return a lost sword to its rightful owner. Chin seeks out the men’s help to take vengeance on the wrongful death of his father.

programme.title: Three Sinners
programme.desc: Based on the classic Ming Dynasty novel The Water Margin, Three Sinners is a Huangmei Opera about love, betrayal, murder, and redemption. Starring Hong Kong's premiere movie couple, it is one of the grandest Eastmancolor-Shawscope costume musicals in the Shaw Brothers library.

programme.title: Pursuit of Vengeance
programme.desc: Kung Fu legend Ti Lung stars in the action movie as Fu Xue Hong, embarking on a epic journey of revenge for his father.

programme.title: Spring Blossoms
programme.desc: Some of Shaw Brothers' biggest female stars of the 1970s share the screen in this tale of young love and interfering parents, starring Lily Li, Shu Pei Pei and Essie Lin Chia.

programme.title: Wild Birds of Australia 1 Ep1
programme.desc: The Little Penguin - Follow the story of Harry and Sally, a pair of little penguins. These flightless, flippered birds create some of the noisiest neighborhoods in nature. Theirs is a family saga of faithful relationships, committed homemaking, and vigorous nightlife.

programme.title: New Kids in the Wild 1 Ep5
programme.desc: Ravi the Baby Lion Tailed Macaque - In India, Ravi the baby lion-tailed macaque faces life in a shrinking habitat and encroaching human world. Luckily he has a caring mum, a protective dad, a playful sister, and numerous, cousins, aunts and uncles all watching over him.

programme.title: Guardians of the Wild 2 Ep3
programme.desc: The Mating Game - Meet Madonna, a very special monkey. She’s the first Kinda baboon ever to be studied from birth to adulthood and now, critically, she’s looking for a mate. Only recently identified as a species in their own right, Kinda baboons are little known and little understood. But Madonna is helping change all that. She may just hold the key to unlocking the secrets of the Kinda’s unique female-male relationships. These are baboons like no others.

programme.title: Guardians of the Wild 2 Ep4
programme.desc: Operation Rhino - Across Africa 97% of black rhinos have been killed for their horns. In 1997 the species was declared officially extinct in Zambia. But now, thanks to an ambitious reintroduction plan, they’re back. Poaching hasn’t gone away – their horns are still prized in Asian medicine. But a small, dedicated team are fighting to keep them safe. This is the frontline of conservation – it doesn’t get any tougher.

programme.title: Battle of the Alphas 1 Ep7
programme.desc: South America - From the Amazon to the Andes, South America has some beautiful scenery. From guanacos sparring over grassland, to marine iguanas head-butting over a beachhead, to home-stealing hermit crabs, the quest for real estate causes a lot of conflict.

programme.title: Africa's Hunters 1 Ep6
programme.desc: Survivors of the Plains - In clans of spotted hyenas, larger females call the shots while smaller males live peripheral lives. Meet a family suffering through drought, a mother struggling to provide for her cubs, and an orphan at the bottom of the social pile.

programme.title: Brazil Untamed 1 Ep5
programme.desc: Cat Country - In many countries the vulnerable and elusive ocelot is on the Endangered Species List. But on the southern edge of the Pantanal, one of the world’s largest tropical wetlands, this magnificent wild cat seems to be making a comeback. A team of young wildlife scientists is trying to understand why.

programme.title: The Big Dry 1 Ep2
programme.desc: Life in the Furnace - It’s October in Zambia’s Luangwa Valley. The hottest and harshest time of year. But this year dry season conditions are exacerbated by a global El Niño event… the Valley is in the throes of drought. There’s been no rain since April and desperate animals are drawn to the only remaining source of water in the Valley – the dwindling Luangwa River. The last remaining deep pools are inhabited by hippos – hundreds squashed together in the only water deep enough to submerge them. As tempers flare and skirmishes break out, it’s a dangerous place for baby hippos, dwarfed by the three-tonne adults.

programme.title: Battle of the Alphas 1 Ep9
programme.desc: USA - The USA is big on flash and spectacle. Bighorn rams rattle the mountaintops. Brown bears battle, desperate to fatten up for winter. Sharp-tailed grouse shake their tail-feathers on the dance floor. Wild stallions rumble with beauty and grace.

programme.title: Battle of the Alphas 1 Ep10
programme.desc: Europe - From the Highlands to the Alps, Europe’s evocative landscapes are the backdrop for epic wildlife drama. Normally stoic red deer go wild during the rut. Wolf packs clash over territory, and foxes do the foxtrot - it’s not as nice as it sounds.

programme.title: Wildlife Icons 2 Ep1
programme.desc: The Clean Up Crew - Every day a struggle for survival plays out across Africa. Predators binge on the dead and nature’s undertakers circle above waiting for their chance. When the mighty fall, an army descends to devour what others leave behind for they too must nurture their precious families.

programme.title: Brazil Untamed 1 Ep6
programme.desc: Amazon Monkeys - In a protected forest on the southern edge of Brazil’s Amazon Rainforest, lives one of the most intelligent and agile monkeys of the New World - the white-whiskered spider monkey. Their long tails are like a 5th limb and they rarely leave the treetops for the forest floor. They are the “ambassadors” of their forest.

programme.title: Wild Birds of Australia 1 Ep2
programme.desc: Secret Life of the Emu - The Emu is Australia’s biggest native bird and is the second largest bird in the world after the African ostrich: two meters tall, with an almost three metre running stride and totally flightless. This bird inhabits a topsy turvy world, where females call the shots, eggs are green and men do all the work to produce and raise tiny babies, known as Stripeys.

programme.title: Weird, Wild & Wonderful
programme.desc: Weird, Wild & Wonderful - Trek across Africa for a peek at the colorful, quirky survival strategies of its animals. See these furry, feathered, and scaled magicians, from flamboyant flamingos to vanishing lizards, find food, elude predators, and find mates against all odds.

programme.title: Battle of the Alphas 1 Ep11
programme.desc: South Africa - Wildebeest battle for herd hierarchy, meerkats live the thug life, floppy fish fight it out on land and locusts give up their vegetarian ways in a frenzy of cannibalism. It all happens on the wild and wide-open landscape of South Africa.

programme.title: Battle of the Alphas 1 Ep12
programme.desc: Sub Sahara - The latitudes south of the Sahara offer vastly different battlegrounds for a wide range of warriors. Male giraffes swing their heads like wrecking balls, zebras boast the most powerful kick in the animal kingdom, and chimpanzee warfare is eerily familiar.

programme.title: Kenya Wildlife Diaries 1 Ep5
programme.desc: A Place in the Wild - Kenya takes a major step with the opening of its first community-run rhino sanctuary in the heart of Samburu territory. The threat to Kenya’s rhinos from armed, illegal poaching gangs is the highest it's been in 40 years, which makes the sanctuary vital.

programme.title: Secret Life of the Koala 1 Ep1
programme.desc: Koala Country - Despite being one of Australia’s best-known marsupials, koalas live only in the east and southeast parts of the continent. Learn how their lives and behaviors vary in these different regions.

programme.title: Africa's Claws & Jaws 1 Ep1
programme.desc: The Predator's Plight - There are animals on earth that are born to kill. Specialized hunters with impressive weapons and unique attack strategies. Every predator has a plight. They must kill to survive. The harsh reality of life as a hunter is never knowing where your next meal is coming from.

programme.title: Africa's Claws & Jaws 1 Ep2
programme.desc: Lethal By Design - Snakes, spiders and scorpions: these creepy crawlies are the animals we connect with least and fear most. While it’s true they have some of the most venomous creatures in the world within their ranks, what is less commonly accepted is that they are often more scared of us then we are of them.

programme.title: Shark Squad 1 Ep1
programme.desc: Island of the White Shark - Off Guadalupe Island, Mexico, top shark ecologist Mauricio Hoyos attempts a television first. Get a unique view as he attaches a camera to the dorsal fin of a great white, revealing how it swims, hunts, and ultimately strikes its prey.

programme.title: Big Cat Country 1 Ep1

programme.title: LIVE: Road To UFC Season 2 Ep1
programme.desc: ROAD TO UFC Season 2 is the most significant opportunity for Asia's top MMA prospects to make it to the world stage. The opening round is divided into four episodes, each of which includes four tournament bouts and one additional non-tournament bout. The event will be held in front of a live audience and the episodes will be produced and distributed for live broadcast using Remote Integration Model production (REMI) from UFC’s state-of-the-art Broadcast Operations Center (BOC) at UFC Apex in Las Vegas in the USA. The event will mark the first live UFC telecasts to be produced entirely remotely, utilizing the new IP-based, 4K-capable BOC and leveraging the expertise of UFC’s full-time production team.
